        "meta_description": "News nominations : Karl Lagerfeld has announced the appointment of Carine Roitfeld as its style adviser for three seasons, starting with Spring/Summer 2020. Roitfeld's role will be to perpetuate the eponymous designer's heritage. (#1084597)",
